T02TD3634E:250a-1: badzra h'um k'a ra s'a dha nam /
T02TD3634E:250a-3: rdo rje h'um mdzad kyi sgrub thabs /
T02TD3634E:250b-0: bcom @250b ldan 'das rdo rje h'um mdzad la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD3634E:250b-1: sngon du gsungs pa'i cho gas nam mkha'i khams su ram yig las skyes pa'i nyi ma la h'um yig 'bar zhing 'bar ba la bskal pa tha ma'i me lta bu shin tu 'bar ba'i mchog tu kha dog gnag pa 'od zer chen po'o //
T02TD3634E:250b-2: de las skyes pa'i drag po chen po khams gsum za bar mdzad pa /
T02TD3634E:250b-3: phyag gnyis rdo rje dang dril bu rab tu sbyor ba'i phyag rgya bcing bar bya'o //
T02TD3634E:250b-4: g-yon brkyang gi zhabs kyis de bzhin du 'jigs byad mnan cing 'jigs par byed pa /
T02TD3634E:250b-7: mgo bo rnams su aom a'a:h'um zhes pa'i yi ge gsum dbang bskur ba'i cho gas thugs rdo rje'i phyag rgya bcing bar bya'o //
T02TD3634E:250b-8: sngags ni aom h'um h'um phat sv'a h'a /
T02TD3634E:250b-9: rdo rje h'um mdzad kyi sgrub thabs rdzogs so//
